This is post 1 of a 3 part series profiling several women in GitLab‚Äôs security organization.  See part two, ["What‚Äôs it like to work in security at GitLab?"](/blog/2021/01/07/whats-it-like-to-work-security-at-gitlab/) and three, ["Considering a career in security? Here‚Äôs some advice."](/blog/2021/03/04/considering-a-career-in-security/).
